566
00:35:15,160 --> 00:35:17,360
Right now, I also have something

567
00:35:17,400 --> 00:35:19,360
I'm waiting to celebrate.

568
00:35:19,760 --> 00:35:22,280
Celebrate what?
Can you tell me first?

569
00:35:22,640 --> 00:35:24,240
If I tell you, it won't be a surprise.

570
00:35:24,240 --> 00:35:25,560
Once you find out,

571
00:35:25,600 --> 00:35:28,280
