592
00:36:33,480 --> 00:36:36,040
I'm not stressed.

593
00:36:36,280 --> 00:36:38,640
I'm just thinking about it.

594
00:36:40,120 --> 00:36:41,440
What are you thinking about?

595
00:36:41,720 --> 00:36:43,600
If something's bothering you,

596
00:36:43,640 --> 00:36:45,400
you can tell me.

597
00:36:49,440 --> 00:36:51,440
I don't know either.

598
00:36:52,200 --> 00:36:55,520
I'm surprised that

599
00:36:56,400 --> 00:36:58,680
when Dad told me that,

600
00:36:59,000 --> 00:37:01,920
I didn't feel sad at all.

601
00:37:03,200 --> 00:37:04,200
Instead,

602
00:37:04,760 --> 00:37:06,080
I actually felt

603
00:37:06,120 --> 00:37:09,400
happy for Song.

604
00:37:10,360 --> 00:37:11,520
Because

605
00:37:12,800 --> 00:37:15,920
