more than I do.

606
00:37:18,080 --> 00:37:19,960
I thought it was something serious.

607
00:37:20,560 --> 00:37:23,240
I'm glad you think that way.

608
00:37:23,960 --> 00:37:27,440
Then should we call and congratulate her?

609
00:37:27,840 --> 00:37:29,760
So I can congratulate her too.

610
00:37:42,840 --> 00:37:43,880
Hey,

611
00:37:44,120 --> 00:37:45,240
I think

612
00:37:45,240 --> 00:37:48,360
I know why I don't feel sad at all.

613
00:37:49,120 --> 00:37:50,240
Why?

614
00:37:50,680 --> 00:37:51,920
Because of you.

615
00:37:53,120 --> 00:37:55,080
- Me?
- Mm-hmm.

616
00:37:57,600 --> 00:37:59,760
I tried imagining

617
00:37:59,800 --> 00:38:01,040
what if

618
00:38:01,480 --> 00:38:03,600
I really became the CEO.

619
00:38:04,880 --> 00:38:07,040
I probably never would've met you.

620
00:38:07,720 --> 00:38:09,960
I wouldn't get to live with you either.

621
00:38:11,200 --> 00:38:12,200
And besides,

622
00:38:12,240 --> 00:38:15,280
