625
00:38:22,360 --> 00:38:24,160
Hearing that

626
00:38:24,400 --> 00:38:26,480
really makes me feel better.

627
00:38:28,880 --> 00:38:30,640
And also,

628
00:38:30,840 --> 00:38:33,440
the project I've been working so hard on

629
00:38:33,480 --> 00:38:36,640
