669
00:40:24,240 --> 00:40:25,640
No problems at all.

670
00:40:25,680 --> 00:40:28,000
Everything is going very well.

671
00:40:28,120 --> 00:40:31,080
It's just that I believe every organization reaches a point

672
00:40:31,120 --> 00:40:33,560
