678
00:40:47,800 --> 00:40:49,000
- I see.
- Yes.

679
00:40:49,040 --> 00:40:50,360
Thank you.

680
00:40:50,920 --> 00:40:52,440
- One photo please.
- Over here please.

681
00:40:52,440 --> 00:40:54,040
I'm so happy for you.

682
00:40:56,280 --> 00:40:58,640
Woo, give us one shot.

683
00:41:01,160 --> 00:41:03,800
Mr. Sujin, what's the second announcement?

684
00:41:03,840 --> 00:41:06,280
For the second announcement,
I think it'd be better

685
00:41:06,320 --> 00:41:09,320
