692
00:41:23,160 --> 00:41:24,840
Not just a living space,

693
00:41:24,880 --> 00:41:26,320
but a place

694
00:41:26,320 --> 00:41:28,920
that supports the dreams
of every generation.

695
00:41:30,560 --> 00:41:32,200
This is my first big step,

696
00:41:32,640 --> 00:41:34,920
and also a new step for S-Mall

697
00:41:34,960 --> 00:41:37,920
