698
00:41:38,640 --> 00:41:39,920
Congratulations.

699
00:41:39,920 --> 00:41:41,480
- A photo please, Ms. Si.
- One photo please.

700
00:41:41,480 --> 00:41:44,280
- This camera please.
- A family photo please, Ms. Si.

701
00:41:44,320 --> 00:41:46,520
- I'm Sujin.
- Ms. Si, Klao, this camera please.

702
00:41:46,560 --> 00:41:49,080
- Ms. Si, Klao, one photo please.
- This camera please.

703
00:41:49,120 --> 00:41:52,000
- Look this way please.
- This camera please.

704
00:41:52,000 --> 00:41:53,520
- This camera please.
- Over here please.

705
00:41:53,560 --> 00:41:56,200
- One more shot this way please.
- This camera please.

706
00:41:56,240 --> 00:41:57,600
Alright, everyone.

707
00:41:57,640 --> 00:42:01,520
I have some fresh good news
to announce today.

708
00:42:02,120 --> 00:42:03,960
Suphan Hom Mali Rice 918,

709
00:42:04,000 --> 00:42:05,200
which is a project for

710
00:42:05,280 --> 00:42:07,640
