715
00:42:18,400 --> 00:42:20,560
- Wow.
- Congratulations.

716
00:42:20,600 --> 00:42:23,440
From now on, Suphan Hom Mali Rice 918

717
00:42:23,600 --> 00:42:26,640
won't just be a product from Thai farmers,

718
00:42:26,640 --> 00:42:28,840
but a source of pride

719
00:42:28,840 --> 00:42:30,760
for Thai people on the world stage.

720
00:42:30,760 --> 00:42:32,800
Congratulations.

721
00:42:32,840 --> 00:42:34,240
Congratulations.

722
00:42:34,240 --> 00:42:35,280
- Look at the camera.
- They're so humble.

723
00:42:35,280 --> 00:42:36,680
- You're amazing.
- Look at the camera please.

724
00:42:36,720 --> 00:42:39,400
- Come here.
- One photo please.

725
00:42:39,440 --> 00:42:42,880
- Very nice.
- Please look this way.

726
00:42:42,920 --> 00:42:46,120
- This camera please.
- This camera too please.

727
00:42:49,400 --> 00:42:50,520
Everyone,

728
00:42:50,920 --> 00:42:52,920
I have something to announce.

729
00:42:53,200 --> 00:42:54,720
Is something wrong?

730
00:42:55,080 --> 00:42:56,120
Seriously.

731
00:42:56,480 --> 00:42:58,800
Why do you suddenly look so serious?

732
00:42:59,040 --> 00:43:00,320
What's going on?

733
00:43:03,640 --> 00:43:06,080
About the lease agreement for the S-Mall land...

734
00:43:06,680 --> 00:43:08,200
I won't be renewing it.

735
00:43:08,240 --> 00:43:09,240
What?

736
00:43:09,880 --> 00:43:11,000
Why?

737
00:43:12,440 --> 00:43:13,680
Klao,

738
00:43:14,440 --> 00:43:16,920
if there's something you're upset with
Mom and Dad about,

739
00:43:17,160 --> 00:43:19,080
we can talk things through calmly.

740
00:43:19,080 --> 00:43:20,440
- Yeah.
- Or...

741
00:43:20,440 --> 00:43:21,640
is it because of me?

742
00:43:21,680 --> 00:43:24,360
Because I became the new CEO instead of Dad,

743
00:43:24,640 --> 00:43:26,960
