746
00:43:30,680 --> 00:43:32,680
You can tell me anything.

747
00:43:33,320 --> 00:43:35,880
Everyone, please calm down.

748
00:43:36,120 --> 00:43:38,160
It's nothing like that at all.

749
00:43:39,920 --> 00:43:42,440
I just wanted to tell everyone that...

750
00:43:44,560 --> 00:43:47,280
well...

751
00:43:52,320 --> 00:43:54,840
I'm transferring the land into Si's name.

752
00:43:54,840 --> 00:43:56,960
What? Hey.

753
00:43:57,840 --> 00:44:00,040
From now on,
if you want to discuss the contract,

754
00:44:00,080 --> 00:44:01,680
