760
00:44:18,680 --> 00:44:22,160
And you're the most precious gift in my life.

761
00:44:24,280 --> 00:44:26,320
As long as I have you by my side,

762
00:44:27,160 --> 00:44:29,040
I don't need anything else.

763
00:44:47,360 --> 00:44:50,640
Tomorrow, let's go transfer the land together.

764
00:44:58,720 --> 00:45:00,360
Hey.

765
00:45:09,600 --> 00:45:10,600
Hey.

766
00:45:11,280 --> 00:45:12,800
Why are you here?

767
00:45:12,880 --> 00:45:16,080
Didn't you say we were going
to the land office?

768
00:45:16,120 --> 00:45:17,920
Weren't we going to transfer the land?

769
00:45:18,120 --> 00:45:20,320
Before we transfer the land,

770
00:45:20,360 --> 00:45:22,440
