774
00:45:33,480 --> 00:45:34,480
Nope.

775
00:45:35,280 --> 00:45:36,280
Huh?

776
00:45:36,640 --> 00:45:38,640
Then what are you looking for?

777
00:45:42,080 --> 00:45:45,520
I hid the key to the cabinet
where the title deed is kept here.

778
00:45:46,920 --> 00:45:49,120
There are so many places you could hide it,

779
00:45:49,360 --> 00:45:51,120
but today you're acting extra weird.

780
00:45:51,120 --> 00:45:53,120
Why would you hide the key here?

781
00:45:53,240 --> 00:45:56,960
This piece of land means a lot to me,

782
00:45:57,000 --> 00:45:59,520
so of course I'd hide something valuable here.

783
00:46:00,640 --> 00:46:03,160
Then let's hurry up and go.

784
00:46:03,200 --> 00:46:05,560
The land office might close before we get there.

785
00:46:05,560 --> 00:46:07,000
Wait, hey.

786
00:46:07,680 --> 00:46:09,640
We can go another day.

787
00:46:09,800 --> 00:46:12,720
That land is going to be yours anyway.

788
00:46:19,280 --> 00:46:20,320
Hey.

789
00:46:20,720 --> 00:46:21,880
What are you doing?

790
00:46:22,600 --> 00:46:24,880
Doing this.

791
00:46:35,240 --> 00:46:36,640
What are you doing here?

792
00:46:36,680 --> 00:46:38,040
Aren't you embarrassed?

793
00:46:39,400 --> 00:46:41,040
No one's gonna see us here.

794
00:46:41,400 --> 00:46:43,840
And even if they did, I wouldn't care.

795
00:47:23,200 --> 00:47:24,200
Hey,

796
00:47:26,040 --> 00:47:27,040
I...

797
00:47:27,680 --> 00:47:29,000
